                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <span id="XSLTPageNoTree123:XSLTOut">
                                <b>This will not be populated when the patient is expressing dissent. If the patient is expressing consent, then this attribute will contain a list of the organs they wish to donate. If a value of "anyOrganTissue" is supplied, then no other values should be present in this attribute.</b>
                            </span>
                            <br/>
                        </p>
                    </text>
