                    <text>
                        <p>
                            <b>A heading for indicating that the patient is the subject of the associated registration information.</b>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <b>This can only be added or updated at the same time as <i>PatientCareProvision</i>, where <i>PatientCareProvision</i>.code is set to '1' (Primary care).</b>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <b>This link shall not be present if <i>PatientCareProvision</i> is being removed, and must be present if <i>PatientCareProvision</i> of type '1' is being added or altered.</b>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <b>The <i>updateMode</i> of the PatientCareProvision class also applies to the RegisteredPatient CMET.</b>
                            <br/>
                        </p>
                    </text>
                </otherAnnotation>
            </annotations>
