                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <span id="XSLTPageNoTree123:XSLTOut">
                                <p>
                                    <b>In addition to the attributes below, in order to control the update semantics, the following will also be present: </b>
                                </p>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>
                                    <b> An <em>updateMode</em> attribute to indicate whether the item should be "added", "altered" or "removed" (mandatory)</b>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </span>
                        </p>
                    </text>
                </otherAnnotation>
            </annotations>
            <attribute conformance="R" fixedValue="OBS"
